.banner-gold .overlay-banner-main .banner-button:focus, .banner-gold .overlay-banner-main .banner-button:hover { color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 209, 59); border: 1px solid rgb(255, 209, 59); }

.banner-gold .overlay-banner-main .banner-button:focus, .banner-gold .overlay-banner-main .banner-button:focus-within { border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 0px 0px 1px inset, rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 0px 0px 2px inset; outline: 0px; }
.banner-gold .overlay-banner-main .banner-button.selected { background-color: rgb(255, 204, 0); border-color: rgb(255, 204, 0); color: rgb(0, 0, 0); }
.banner-gold .overlay-banner-mini .frb-submit { color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(139, 139, 139); border: 1px solid rgb(139, 139, 139); }

.banner-gold .overlay-banner-mini .frb-submit:focus, .banner-gold .overlay-banner-mini .frb-submit:hover { color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 209, 59); border: 1px solid rgb(255, 209, 59); }

.banner-gold .overlay-banner-mini .frb-submit:focus, .banner-gold .overlay-banner-mini .frb-submit:focus-within { border-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-shadow: rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 0px 0px 1px inset, rgb(255, 255, 255) 0px 0px 0px 2px inset; outline: 0px; }

.banner-gold .overlay-banner-mini.visible .frb-conversation-close, .banner-gold .overlay-banner-mini.visible .frb-conversation-open { border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(127, 123, 116) rgb(127, 123, 116) rgb(18, 18, 18); border-image: initial; background-color: rgb(18, 18, 18); top: -48px; }
